channel.title: The real runescape multi Log tutorial-Pics-
channel.description:
This tutorial will further show you how to multi Log onto runescape: Step 1.
[ul][li]Open Runescape and load it normally into a world[/li] [li]Open up a second page and go to "Detail select" And scroll down to the drop down box,Click unsigned java[/ul]
[IMG]http://i20.tinypic.com/2yp0tih.jpg[/img] Step 2: Have the two pages open of course.
[ul][li]The unsigned applet will take longer because well..it just does[/li] [li]I hope you liked this simple guide on how to multi-log[/li][/ul]
[size=20pt]The purpose of this post: [/size]Don't Drop trade and lose ur items like I did! Be safer! Multi Log!

item.dc:creator: @xxlegitxx xxlegitxx
item.description:
@xxlegitxx wrote:

[quote=“D3athtousall, post:7, topic:151569”]Lol,

me friend didnt want to drop trade and wanted a tank.

So he got alot of arrows, bows, xbos, bolts, 10mill ect ect.

He didnt want to drop trade so at school we went in the library and used 2 comp to trade on both account.

Everyone stared in amazment.

Being the only smart one there, I went on the comp across from it, went on rs, went to change pass, saw his pass, changed it, waited, saw his recoverys, used em to get pass, changed recoverys and pass, went on his account and went for a joy ride.

=P He was my friend so I gave back.

+Took a few mill and blue h’ween mask that he scammed from me+[/quote]

How exactly did you ‘see’ his pass and ‘see’ his recoveries?

[quote=“predalienrunner, post:6, topic:151569”]No it shouldn’t get you banned… unless you trade 10 million gp for nothing. They account for internet cafes and hooked up computers which all have the same ip.
also use search to find threads on other ways and that delve into a bit more detail.[/quote]

Yea don’t worry about getting banned. If you want to make sure you’re safe, use Tor. It’s what I use when I scam accounts.
